[35m│[0m capability not only helps in honing cybersecurity skills but also in         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m identifying potential vulnerabilities that might exist in real-world         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m systems.\n        <br/><br/>\n        In the realm of autonomous pentesting, [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m AI proves invaluable by automating the process of vulnerability scanning and [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m exploitation. Traditional pentesting can be time-consuming and               [35m│[0m
