[35m│[0m applications and systems, AI-powered pentesters offer significant            [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m advantages. These systems can process and analyze large volumes of code and  [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m network traffic, pinpointing vulnerabilities that might be missed by human   [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m testers. By leveraging natural language processing and advanced pattern      [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m recognition, AI can uncover subtle bugs and logic flaws that pose            [35m│[0m
